      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EYE CAN EAR AMOUR (10) is racing well and deserves a win after placing in four of his last five starts, three of those coming at this circuit and distance. Chased a smart one when runner-up last time. Must overcome a very wide draw but this is winnable if things go his way. AGENTOFGOODINTENT (1) has been good from wider barriers in both starts since a spell. Well served by the ace draw and should be peaking. ENOLA (2) led from this barrier and stuck on for fourth against the fillies last start at this circuit and distance. Building in fitness and can push forward again to give a sight. CONCILIATE (6) found the Nutrien Classic Sales series beyond her but this is easier and her best form has come at the mile. Fitter for recent racing and could show more. SNIPERS FIRE (9) draws wide and broke last time so will need to get it right but will be fitter third up and showed good ability last campaign.",
